- FRED timeout noted (2Y yield = prior close); Stooq 404s and the GOOG/GOOGL/HON/OLN/SCCO anomaly flags surfaced in the Sources footer — GOOG/GOOGL treated as real since corroborated by earnings headlines.
- Noted the minor VIX discrepancy (snapshot 17.93 vs. Market Context 18.23) rather than papering over it.

